text:
HollywoodLife routinely makes up fake news stories about Selena Gomez , including tales about how she would like to “double date” with a slew of other celebrity couples. The current one involves a proposed double date with Gomez and The Weeknd and her friend Taylor Swift and new boyfriend Joe Alwyn . But like its previous reports, […]
